Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.74,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,146)}3小時前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:08.23,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(286,89)}（華盛頓DC IMF本部\N\h\hG20臨時首腦會議(非正式)）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:11.87,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(108,151)}（IMF理事專務）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:06.66,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The rapid changes in the market in southeast Asia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:06.66,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,…東南亞洲市場的急速變化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:10.66,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,is sure to trigger a large financial crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:10.66,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,將很有可能引發一場大型金融危機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.54,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,We are desperately seeking funds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.54,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,我們急需融資
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:17.54,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that a direct result of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:17.54,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的變動難道不是因為「那個」嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.79,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no hard evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.79,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我們目前情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:21.38,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no way for telling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:21.38,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,無法推測其是否存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.38,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The financial district
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.38,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,金融街…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:27.13,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our organization's bureaucratics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:27.13,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,…如果我們的一位財務官員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.30,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,has access to it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.30,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,潛入金融街了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:34.64,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,You all have heard the Caribbean republic and Caribbeans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:34.64,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都知道一個叫加勒比共和國的事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:36.93,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,As a rumor，yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:36.93,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞的話  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.19,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.19,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.69,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's actually seen or heard of it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.69,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒人親眼看見或者親耳聽到這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.53,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared because South America finance district collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.53,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的消失是因為南美金融街的破產
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.36,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lehman shock was a direct result to this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.36,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,雷曼衝擊也是其所造成的直接後果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.29,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who have access,call this 「C」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.29,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,出入金融街的人們稱它為 「C」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:55.91,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:55.91,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.75,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that going to happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.75,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,「C」會再次發生嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.25,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It can happen at anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.25,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,它隨時都有可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:02.09,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,can't say exactly when
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:02.09,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,但無法預估其確切時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.04,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.04,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:14.72,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The time，might come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:14.72,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時間…似乎已經到來…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:18.47,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(111,149)}（東南亞洲金融街）

